from test: 41 The results discussed above do not support a mechanism where a major portion of the Cl− in the oxide film resulted from entrainment of Cl− during oxide growth but rather Cl− moves into the oxide film.
from Soup: 41 The results discussed above do not support a mechanism where a major portion of the Cl − in the oxide film resulted from entrainment of Cl − during oxide growth but rather Cl − moves into the oxide film.
